Another and simpler alternative would be exposing it directly in `InterProcessReadWriteLock`:
```
    protected String getLockPath()
    {
        final var lockPath = readMutex.getLockPath();
        if (lockPath != null) {
            return lockPath;
        }
        return writeMutex.getLockPath();
    }
```
